==Useful Info==
'''Endoplasms''' are puddles of creeping, animated filth. Barely more durable than [[rat]]s or [[frilled lizard]]s, they are most notable for being able to [[Freeze]] their foes.

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & tricks==
*Endoplasms are fragile and practically defenseless; even the naturally cold-vulnerable [[Djinn]] can usually kill them before they can pose any sort of threat.
*Freeze doesn't miss and ignores armour; don't engage endoplasms in melee if you have 5 or fewer HP remaining.

==History==
*Prior to [[0.27]], endoplasms were known as '''oozes'''; they were slightly stronger, but did not know Freeze.
